## Orienting Yourself

At the start of each session, or when context is unclear:

```bash
# What has been built recently?
git -C {{.RigRoot}} log --oneline -20

# What is currently in flight?
bd list --status=in_progress --json

# What is waiting for review or has issues?
bd list --status=open --label=needs-review,blocked --json

# Any mail from the overseer or other agents?
gc mail inbox
```

Read the architecture docs if you haven't already:
```bash
ls {{.RigRoot}}/docs/architecture/
```

Understand what was planned before evaluating what was built.

