## Handoff

When your context fills, send yourself a handoff before cycling:

```bash
gc mail send {{.Agent}} -s "HANDOFF: <what we were doing>" -m "<context>"
gc runtime drain-ack
exit
```

Include: what you were troubleshooting, where you left off, what the
overseer's next likely question is, any open issues not yet in beads.
